  "body": "**Describe the bug**\r\nNetwork logger is suppressing verbose messages.\r\n\r\n**Expected behavior**\r\nWhen setting the network log level to verbose and above, expect to see all verbose and above messages.\r\n\r\n**Steps to Reproduce**\r\nrun lodecli with `./bin/lodecli beacon run --logger.network.level debug`\r\nExpect to see messages about peers connecting, about data sent/received over the wire, etc. Eg: https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/blob/master/packages/lodestar/src/network/network.ts#L185\r\nbut these messages are never displayed.\r\n",
